snippet.title: Jason Momoa Reacts To Amber Heard NOT Being Fired From Aquaman!
snippet.description:
Celebrities Like Jason Momoa React To Finding Out That Amber Heard Was NOT Fired From Aquaman And Will Continue Playing The Role Of Mera!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

It seems Jason Momoa has recently joined the long list of celebrities who are fed up with Amber Heard and don't want to do anything with her anymore. Apparently, Jason has finally reached his limit and has started taking action so Amber Heard finally leaves her role as Mera in Aquaman 2. Him and Amber met way back in 2018 when both starred in the movie Aquaman, their relationship has been strictly professional and they have managed to work smoothly alongside each other. Jason has also tried to stay away from Amber’s personal life not to get involved in her drama. But recent revelations seem to indicate that Jason has had enough and has started to take matters into his own hands to remove her from the movie. But how exactly has he been trying to push her away?
